I don't have a dad.

00:28.081 --> 00:30.860
Maybe some other time.
Lose yourself, baby.

00:31.026 --> 00:33.213
Lose yourself. Just you and me.

00:33.333 --> 00:35.505
And me.
Here's the specs you wanted, Mel.

00:35.621 --> 00:38.398
Oh, jeez. Sorry. I gotta get back to work.

00:38.530 --> 00:40.442
Baby, that was crazy good, though.
Yeah?

00:40.567 --> 00:43.770
Yeah. You know what's crazy gooder?
This sweet j-o-b.

00:43.888 --> 00:44.924
