ears on the Comic-Con floor.

02:35.076 --> 02:37.206
And no, I will not pay for a Batmobile.

02:37.332 --> 02:41.098
Ooh! Okay, now me. Now me. What's my job?
Your job is gonna be

02:41.196 --> 02:43.610
