monitoring security feed.

02:43.729 --> 02:46.617
Cameron, your job is gonna
be to hand-deliver the film,

02:46.749 --> 02:48.227
stay there until they finish the screening,

02:48.332 --> 02:49.964
then return it here to contra safely.

02:50.083 --> 02:52.402
