03:08.580 --> 03:11.047
You are too close to this.
It's like my daddy always said--

03:11.183 --> 03:13.750
Don't give the pill popper
keys to the pharmacy.

03:13.910 --> 03:16.719
He was a pill popper... and a pharmacist.

03:16.842 --> 03:18.430
Do we, uh, at least get to watch it?

03:18.553 --> 03:19.978
