07:43.751 --> 07:45.614
No! No, no, no, no. Any time but now.

07:45.744 --> 07:48.244
Yo, melon balls! Where are you, girl?

07:48.531 --> 07:50.266
Cam, what's up?

07:50.386 --> 07:53.298
