is sort of a dick move, if you ask me.

14:27.556 --> 14:30.202
All right, but you--you saw that Cash
was at Comic-Con.

14:30.203 --> 14:31.126
You saw the footage, right?
Yes,

14:31.127 --> 14:33.609
