The bad news is our thief made a web
site that went live this morning.

15:00.799 --> 15:04.296
In eight hours, he promises to upload
the stolen movie for the world to see.

15:04.297 --> 15:05.936
Now if we don't track this guy,

15:06.105 --> 15:07.884
the studio's holding us responsible.

15:07.885 --> 15:10.021
So how are we going to fix this?

15:10.158 --> 15:13.067
We can't, but I know who can.

15:14.017 --> 15:15.944
Can I get everyone's attention, please?

15:16.495 --> 15:19.284
Last night, I accused a good
friend of something he didn't do.

15:20.183 --> 15:22.723
Truth is, I hacked my way into college,

15:22.724 --> 15:24.448
where I hid out for the last seven years.

15:24.449 --> 15:26.879
I was fine with not
having any real friends,

15:27.177 --> 15:31.153
and being so set in my ways
has caused me to hurt someone

15:31.829 --> 15:33.317
I really care about.

15:34.524 --> 15:37.246
And for that... I'm sorry.

15:38.796 --> 15:42.124
Look, we have five hours
to get this movie back,

15:42.125 --> 15:44.656
and that may seem
impossible, but not for us.

15:45.099 --> 15:47.278
All right, this is our time!

15:47.427 --> 15:50.160
It's our time in here, and you know why?

15:50.765 --> 15:52.778
Because goonies never say "Die."

15:55.005 --> 15:56.561
You watched the movie?

15:57.463 --> 15:59.249
Does this answer your question?

15:59.259 --> 16:02.456
No. Don't...
Don't do that unless you mean it.

16:02.663 --> 16:04.211
Truffle shuffle, baby.

16:25.458 --> 16:26.649
That was beautiful.

16:30.570 --> 16:32.099
All right, buddy.

16:32.100 --> 16:33.794
There's only one person who can get inside

16:33.795 --> 16:35.468
the mind of the geek who stole this movie.

16:36.750 --> 16:39.033
This seems like a job for Black Zeus.

16:40.661 --> 16:43.372
The Zeus is loose.

16:46.676 --> 16:48.278
That's his catchphrase.

16:55.534 --> 16:58.802
All right, so I've gamed up
every possible situation,

16:58.803 --> 17:00.239
and this is what I've come up with.

17:00.904 --> 17:03.210
Our thief is feeling pretty cool

17:03.211 --> 17:05.300
that he's seen something
that no one else has,

17:05.300 --> 17:09.602
but what would any geek want to
see more than a "Goonies" sequel?

17:09.835 --> 17:12.490
Only two things--
"Megan Fox

17:12.491 --> 17:14.934
Warrior Princess."

17:14.935 --> 17:18.852
So we give 'em both--
Megan Fox as Xena.

17:19.678 --> 17:21.357
The perfect storm.

17:21.376 --> 17:24.222
What if there was a pirated
rough cut of a Xena movie

17:24.223 --> 17:27.123
that no one knew about, and
we were willing to trade?

17:27.337 --> 17:29.652
No nerd alive would ever turn that down.

17:29.943 --> 17:32.428
But where are we gonna find
someone who looks like Megan Fox?

17:37.097 --> 17:39.078
Oh. Damn it.

17:39.567 --> 17:40.533
Fine.

17:40.534 --> 17:42.420
Where are you gonna find
a Xena costume on such--

17:43.150 --> 17:44.583
Damn it.

17:45.031 --> 17:46.681
And... action.

17:48.647 --> 17:49.943
I know you guys are fighting.

17:49.944 --> 17:52.578
Mel, you're feeling smothered,
but you guys gotta lock lips.

17:52.579 --> 17:55.865
Come on, guys. We need this.
Grab Hercules in your arms...

17:55.866 --> 17:58.714
And kiss him like your life depended on it.

17:58.868 --> 18:00.786
I mean, you just look so ridiculous.

18:00.905 --> 18:03.583
Yeah?
Yeah, and you look... hot.

18:06.864 --> 18:08.166
Baby, I'm an idiot.

18:08.167 --> 18:10.475
I know, but I love you anyway.

18:11.226 --> 18:13.276
24/siete, baby.

18:16.175 --> 18:19.047
All right, I think we got it.
I think we got it. Let's cut.

18:19.048 --> 18:21.192
No, let the scene play.

18:21.347 --> 18:24.556
Everybody, out! Get out! Out now! Go!

18:24.557 --> 18:26.316
Sparta!

18:28.820 --> 18:30.566
Okay, our thief really
knows what he's doing.

18:30.567 --> 18:32.655
His goonileaks web site is untraceable.

18:32.656 --> 18:34.662
But he's been all over the message boards,

18:34.663 --> 18:36.963
bragging about his conquest.
That's how we'll trap him.

18:37.069 --> 18:38.638
Did our little fishy take the bait?

18:39.194 --> 18:40.534
Oh, yeah.

18:40.861 --> 18:44.001
All right. Van's gassed up. Let's do this.

18:44.174 --> 18:46.787
Dude, what is wrong with your face?

18:46.788 --> 18:48.285
What's right with yours?

18:49.572 --> 18:51.153
Oh, my God.

18:52.167 --> 18:55.934
Baby, the Xena kiss.
I forgot about your peanut allergy.

18:56.064 --> 18:57.760
Let me see. Hey.

18:57.761 --> 18:59.046
I regret nothing.

18:59.349 --> 19:00.213
Oh.

19:03.668 --> 19:06.422
All right, Black Zeus, eyes open.
He's out there.

19:06.423 --> 19:07.466
Everyone in position?

19:07.538 --> 19:08.695
Check.

19:09.585 --> 19:10.763
Check.

19:11.970 --> 19:13.083
Check.

19:13.858 --> 19:14.857
Check.

19:15.442 --> 19:16.581
Check.

19:17.549 --> 19:20.113
Target acquired.
You got a tortoise on your tail.

19:20.337 --> 19:22.068
Don't be a hero, Cash.

19:22.403 --> 19:24.668
I'm gonna have turtle soup tonight.

19:34.982 --> 19:36.037
Okay.

19:36.599 --> 19:38.002
On three, we trade.

19:42.822 --> 19:43.643
Come on.
Hey.

19:43.644 --> 19:44.821
Wait your turn.

19:45.581 --> 19:48.272
One, two...

19:50.479 --> 19:53.055
Got a broken arrow. Go, go, go, go.

19:56.031 --> 19:58.617
Hey, you guys!

19:59.067 --> 20:01.711
That doesn't sound anything like Sloth.
This guy sucks!

20:05.090 --> 20:07.457
Go, go, go, go, go! Move! Move!

20:12.862 --> 20:13.993
Where is he? Where?

20:15.858 --> 20:18.224
Well, he shed his shell.
He could be anyone here,

20:18.225 --> 20:19.966
damn it.
He got away with both DVDs.

20:20.435 --> 20:21.453
Oh, did he?

20:22.739 --> 20:24.405
Sleight of hand.

20:25.610 --> 20:27.382
Magic Camp, suckas.

20:27.383 --> 20:29.792
Three, two, one.

20:30.773 --> 20:32.933
Yeah! And the countdown is over.

20:32.934 --> 20:35.410
We have the movie. Nice work, people.

20:35.430 --> 20:37.058
And I just got off the
horn with the studio.

20:37.059 --> 20:40.106
Not only did you rescue their
film from a mutant fanboy,

20:40.201 --> 20:42.974
but you garnered them a
ton of free publicity.

20:42.975 --> 20:46.904
If I had a tail, I'd be wagging it.
Cheers! Cheers!

20:48.032 --> 20:49.607
All right!
Hey, uh,

20:49.608 --> 20:50.959
you, uh, wanna hang tonight?

20:50.960 --> 20:53.206
Maybe grab a beer, watch the Laker game?

20:53.207 --> 20:57.856
No, I was thinking more along the
lines of "Harry Potter"-thon. You in?

20:58.141 --> 20:59.719
I'm in like Slytherin.

20:59.939 --> 21:02.743
All right. Warlocks, abracadabra,

21:02.874 --> 21:04.657
that kid from... I don't know.

21:05.074 --> 21:07.235
You're trying. That's good.

